{"title":"ocean_contributions_help","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"markdown":"* This panel focuses on **Engagement** in terms of **number of contributions**.
* **Heat map** allows to find most active organizations and which projects they are targeting their contributions to.
* **Bar charts** show evolution of contributions in total and stacked by data source and allows to identify the general trend and local trends based on moving averages.

[See complete panel documentation](https://chaoss.github.io/grimoirelab-sigils/panels/engagement-contributions-overview/)"},"aggs":[]}
